snippet.title: HYPER DRONE X
snippet.description:
A high-tech drone racing game that's fun for the whole family!
Pass around Joy-Con controllers and compete with up to four players!

Find your favorite among more than twenty drones to choose from!

Race through buildings, cities, nature, and more!
Lots of unique courses to discover!

Steer through rings to get a boost of speed!
Use dash items and fly rings to accelerate ahead of your opponents!

Gyro controls available too!
Let your hands guide you!
